100100.describe_illustrated_guid:
I'm Olympic... I'm in charge of the island's flour mill.
It always smells like wheat flour here, and the turning of the mill is like a lullaby... It makes it so easy to doze off. If you want some flour, just bring me some wheat... Mmh... Zzz...
100100.name: Olympic

100200.describe_illustrated_guid:
I'm Patrick, manager of the logistics center.
Be it harbor requests, managing the cargo ship schedule, or keeping our trade ledger up to date, I'm your girl.
I guarantee your resources will move around as smooth as the sea breeze blows!
100200.name: Patrick

100300.describe_illustrated_guid:
Hey there! I'm Stephen!
I miiight hide behind a shipping container and slack off sometimes, but don't worry!
I'll handle anything you need, whether it's building materials or crops!
Be sure to give me a call the next time you come to the harbor!
100300.name: Stephen

100400.describe_illustrated_guid: Commander, I'm Homeric. The seeds on the farm are growing quietly, nourished by rain and sunshine. All we have to do is wait patiently for the land to bless us with its gifts.
100400.name: Homeric

100500.describe_illustrated_guid:
Baa! Moo! I'm Amerigo, the island's happy-go-lucky rancher!
I spend my days surrounded by fluffy li'l critters, collecting eggs, milking cows, and chasing after runaway lambs. It's hectic, but I love it!
Whenever you've got a moment to spare, you should totally drop by the ranch!
100500.name: Amerigo

100600.describe_illustrated_guid:
Commander, over here! I'm John, and I'll show you around the place!
This mine is so fascinating, and well worth exploring! Once you're ready, let's ride the minecart in and have a look around!
Also, I'm gonna sing you a special song dedicated to the mine opening, so look forward to that!
100600.name: John

100700.describe_illustrated_guid:
I'm O'Brien, and I'm fighting tooth and nail for the island's development.
You probably don't know this, but whenever work's left me feeling exhausted, I secretly think of you. It makes me happy, no matter how tough the logging gets.
100700.name: O'Brien

100800.describe_illustrated_guid:
Commander, I am Am-Mer-Mar. I oversee the harbor's commercial area.
I'm detail-oriented, and I do everything from daily balance checks, optimizing the store displays, and analyzing customer trends. There is no sense of accomplishment quite like seeing the commercial area prosper.
100800.name: Am-Mer-Mar

100900.describe_illustrated_guid:
What's up, Commander? I'm Russell! I run the development area's factory!
To my ears, there's no better music than the mechanical rumble of a running assembly line!
Although the wrenches tend to go missing here and progress often gets delayed, I'll run the machinery at full power whenever you need it!
100900.english_name: SS Brigadier General Clinton W. Russell
100900.name: Russell

101000.describe_illustrated_guid:
I am Elizabeth, the receptionist of Get-Together Island.
For the time being, I will be your guide around the island as well as your assistant in development.
I shall assist you as best as I can with construction so that this can be a safe, comfortable place for all the islanders to flourish.
101000.name: Elizabeth

101100.describe_illustrated_guid:
Rays of the sun♪ Dew on the leaves♪ Succulent fruit, grow and grow big♪ I'm Lusitania, the manager of the orchard!
Seeing the fruit ripen and change color little by little just makes me think, "Wow, the world's such a wonderful place!"
101100.name: Lusitania

101200.describe_illustrated_guid:
Hi, Commander. I'm Bremen. I work at Café Manjuu by the harbor.
I love the air in here – and the smell of coffee in it. Just watching the vapor slowly rise into the air every day makes me feel at ease.
And, um, whenever you drop by, I'll have a seat ready for you to enjoy some quiet.
101200.name: Bremen

101300.describe_illustrated_guid:
Testing, testing... I'm Mary, your cutest and most energetic guide on Get-Together Island!
I show all visitors around with a bright smile, and give them a taste of all the fun and enthusiasm this island has to offer!
101300.name: Mary

101400.describe_illustrated_guid:
I'm Laconia... I look after the plant nursery and the bees on the island.
When the sun shines, it's dead quiet in the nursery, and the only thing you can hear are the bees... That's what I really like.
Commander, I just harvested some honey... Want a taste? It's really sweet.
101400.name: Laconia

101600.describe_illustrated_guid:
I'm Peary, the seasonal manager. I'm currently putting together a list of materials needed for development.
Lately, I've been thinking about the new development plan, and I'd love to hear some of your thoughts. Although the island still has a long way to develop, we will follow the path slowly and steadily.
101600.name: Peary

1011000.describe_illustrated_guid: Commander! I drew an exploration map of the island! Sure, it's a little rough, but I promise it'll lead you to treasure this time! Believe me!
1011000.name: William D. Porter

1020500.describe_illustrated_guid: The breeze is calm and the sun is shining... You know, I just poured some new afternoon tea. Why don't you stay for a while and have a drink?
1020500.name: Helena

1051700.describe_illustrated_guid: Whether on the battlefields or out in the woods, the Indomitable Black Dragon is the strongest! Honey, come with me as we rise to the top of the world!
1051700.name: New Jersey

1070300.describe_illustrated_guid: Sister Sara is here with the bounties of sky and earth! Commander, would you like to try some of the veggies I grew myself? I promise you, they're delicious AND nutritious!
1070300.name: Saratoga

2040300.describe_illustrated_guid: The Royal Navy's elegance is one thing that shall never be tarnished by the passage of time. Commander, would you like to share in the whispers of our coming victories over a cup of tea?
2040300.name: Hood

2060300.describe_illustrated_guid: B-Big Brother, I-I'm really happy to be able to help out like this! I'll keep w-working hard, because... I-I love you the most!
2060300.name: Unicorn

2990300.describe_illustrated_guid: Ownerrr~ I can feel your passionate gaze lingering on Cheshire again... and I love it! Look at me as much as you want, and only at me! Meow~♡
2990300.name: Cheshire

3012900.describe_illustrated_guid: Whether it comes to delivering goods, harvesting crops, or providing support, speed is always key! That's why you should leave it to me, your speed-star Shimakaze! It's just that easy!
3012900.name: Shimakaze

3031200.describe_illustrated_guid: Work? Missions? Who cares! Those can wait, but my lap pillow is only available here and now. Come, enjoy a little afternoon nap with me.
3031200.name: {namecode:67}

3040700.describe_illustrated_guid: Caring for every little tree on this island... is how I protect my loved ones now! Commander, please watch as these fruit trees grow strong and ripe!
3040700.name: Amagi-chan

3070700.describe_illustrated_guid: My Commander~ No matter where we are, I will always be yours, and yours alone. So, be sure to cherish that, okay? ❤
3070700.name: Taihou

3120100.describe_illustrated_guid: Nyahaha~ The all-capable Akashi can use all the latest technology to upgrade your tools, nya! All it requires is a bit of compensation for the R&D costs and the materials~ Quite the good deal, nya?
3120100.name: Akashi

4030300.describe_illustrated_guid: Commander, would you like to try this special cocktail I prepared just for you? ...Heehee, don't worry. It has a unique flavor that will leave you with an... unforgettable aftertaste.
4030300.name: Prinz Eugen

4990200.describe_illustrated_guid: Turning our positions on the battlefield into a courtyard layout... This place is our new world, my child. All you need to do is bask in the stillness, while I'll handle everything else.
4990200.name: {namecode:440}

5020400.describe_illustrated_guid: The tea is ready, and the inkstick has been ground. Commander, could I bother you to set aside your work for a moment and come appreciate this work-in-progress painting with me?
5020400.name: Ying Swei

5020500.describe_illustrated_guid: Ugh! How many times do I have to remind you... I'M the big sister here! You better remember it, Commander, or I'll get mad!
5020500.name: Chao Ho

5060100.describe_illustrated_guid: The pieces have come to a halt, yet this small patch of grassland has its own charms. Why not treat managing the island as a game of Go unto itself? For now, I wish simply to drink tea with you and gaze at the flowers.
5060100.name: Chen Hai

6080200.describe_illustrated_guid: Commander, this place is chock-full of inspiration and my brain's already firing on all cylinders! If there's anything you need doing, I'm your girl!
6080200.name: Leonardo da Vinci

7010400.describe_illustrated_guid: The sky-blue trail ever continues to stretch into the distant horizon. But rather than traveling alone, I now look forward to being able to share this moment of tranquility with my comrades.
7010400.name: Tashkent

9011100.describe_illustrated_guid: I know I said "I'll do whatever," but the scope of this work is a bit too much... *yaaawn*... Commander, just lemme nap for five minutes... Just five... more minutes...
9011100.name: Le Malin
